            <title>台湾智能取色器，吸取实体颜色即时转换成数据</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/02/onemade-huion/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=onemade-huion</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/02/onemade-huion/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 02:46:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1196666</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>为了能让设计师或其他有需要者更能准确选取颜色搭配，台湾电子公司 ONEmade 联合 HUION 推出「色计师智能取色器」，帮助人们解决视觉色差困难。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.27-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196839" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.27-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.27-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.27-1280x719.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.27-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.27-1536x863.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.27-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.37.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196840" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.37-694x550.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="550" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.37-694x550.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.37-1135x900.jpg 1135w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.37-768x609.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-10-02-上午 10.43.37.jpg 1196w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>ONEmade 与 HUION 合作推出的「色计师智能取色器」可配合手机 App，快速获得色彩的各项参数，并取得实体物品颜色的 RGB、CMYK、Delta E 以及 Pantone 色码。</p><p>而取色器的外貌大小与 iPhone 充电插头相约，用家可随身携带，当有需要时将取色器的镜头放在要检测颜色的纸面、墙面或衣物及各项物品上，然后按一下机身顶端上的按钮，取色器便会自动记录目标颜色，并传送到手机内 App 以便用家获取资讯。</p><p>另外，取色器还会以客观数据进行配色建议，可持续扫描超过 10,000 次、续航力佳，并搭配 2 合 1 触控笔座。此外，所配合应用程式 iOS 、Android 版的个人电脑或其他装置蓝牙 5.0 等最高版本，可用于 Photoshop、 Illustrator 、Indesign 与 Expresii 等影像处理软件，且支援可编辑 Hex 色码的软件，如 Paint 3D、Paint S、FotoJet 等。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_37818"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/5sDNsGFDiww?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.zeczec.com/projects/onemade-colordesigner?r=fed674bcce">zeczec</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
